<br>
<br>
<br>
I couldnt defeat the stupid marionette pig at first and ultimately reset cause he wasn't hurting me and I wasn't hurting him. I figured it out eventually. The crazy catepillar was the toughest though. Final Ganon sure got what's coming to him though. Wait till you see what he does. <br>
<br>
<br>
Spoiler II<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
For those of you who haven't beaten it or just dont care, Link shoves the master sword almost all the way into Ganon's skull. Then he turns to stone. Hilarious!! And fitting....<br>
<br>
<br>
End Spoilers.<br>
<br>
